title: Douglas Adams (read by Adams) - All 5 books of the Hitchhiker
description:
The five audiobooks for the five books of the Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy series, written and read by Douglas Adams.

1. The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy

2. The Restaurant at the End of the Universe.

3. Life, the Universe and Everything
 
4. So Long and Thanks for All the Fish

5. Mostly Harmless


The five Hitchhiker's books, read by Douglas Adams, the author. They are each in separate folders, so you can easily choose which ones you want to download. They are all consistently tagged and named. The 1st and 3rd book are on a single track, where the others are each split into 8 tracks. Each one is somewhere around 5 hours long.
